Title: An Antlered Skull
Description:
<Despite its surroundings, this skull does not appear to be fel-corrupted.

As you move your hand closer, you feel a sense of calm emanating from it. 

Soridormi will want to see this.>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Antlered Skull to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return the Antlered Skull to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
